2e^{i(\pi/4)}
\sqrt2e^{i(-\pi/4)}
2e^{i(\pi/2)}
1+i
\frac{(2i+2)(1+i)}{1^2+1^2}
i^2=-1
\frac{2i+2}{1-i} =\frac{2i+2}{1-i}\frac{1+i}{1+i}=\frac{2(1+i)(1+i)}{1-i^2}=\frac{(1+i^2)}{1+1}=1+2i+i^2=1+2-1=2i.
\frac{1+i}{1-i}=\frac{2\sqrt{2}(\sqrt{2}/2+i\sqrt{2}/2)}{\sqrt{2}(\sqrt{2}/2-i\sqrt{2}/2)} =2\frac{e^{i\frac{\pi}{4}}}{e^{-i\frac{\pi}{4}}}=2e^{i\frac{\pi}{2}}=2i?
